# 路由与导航 Skills

## 模块概述
项目使用 React Router v6 实现客户端路由，支持嵌套路由和动态参数。

## 核心文件
- `src/app/App.tsx` - 路由配置
- `src/app/components/Layout.tsx` - 布局组件
- `src/app/components/ProjectSidebar.tsx` - 项目侧边栏导航

## 路由结构

```typescript
// 位置: src/app/App.tsx
<Routes>
  {/* 首页 - 书架 */}
  <Route path="/" element={<Layout />}>
    <Route index element={<Bookshelf />} />
    
    {/* 项目详情 */}
    <Route path="projects/:projectId" element={<ProjectDetail />} />
    
    {/* 项目数据统计 */}
    <Route path="projects/:projectId/dashboard" element={<ProjectDashboard />} />
    
    {/* 导演风格 */}
    <Route path="projects/:projectId/style" element={<DirectorStyleEditor />} />
    
    {/* 项目库 */}
    <Route path="projects/:projectId/assets" element={<AssetLibrary />} />
    
    {/* 章节原文编辑 */}
    <Route path="projects/:projectId/chapter/:chapterId" element={<ChapterEditor />} />
    
    {/* 剧本编辑 */}
    <Route path="projects/:projectId/script/:chapterId" element={<ScriptEditor />} />
    
    {/* 分镜制作 */}
    <Route path="projects/:projectId/storyboard/:chapterId" element={<StoryboardEditor />} />
    
    {/* 系统设置 */}
    <Route path="settings" element={<Settings />} />
  </Route>
</Routes>
```

## 路由参数

```typescript
// 获取路由参数
import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom';

const { projectId, chapterId } = useParams<{
  projectId: string;
  chapterId: string;
}>();
```

## 导航方式

### 声明式导航
```tsx
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

<Link to={`/projects/${projectId}`}>项目详情</Link>
<Link to={`/projects/${projectId}/script/${chapterId}`}>剧本编辑</Link>
```

### 编程式导航
```typescript
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

const navigate = useNavigate();

// 跳转
navigate(`/projects/${projectId}`);

// 替换历史记录
navigate(`/projects/${projectId}`, { replace: true });

// 返回
navigate(-1);
```

